  "story_segments": [
    "Giant pandas are perhaps ",
    " most famous animals in the world. They live in the high mountains of China, ",
    " it is cool and wet.\n\nPandas are very good ",
    " climbing trees. They spend most of ",
    " day eating bamboo. A panda can eat for 12 hours ",
    " day! Although they look like bears, they ",
    " eat much meat.\n\nIn the past, there were ",
    " many pandas in the wild, but now the number is growing ",
    " people are protecting the forests. When a baby panda is born, it is very small. It is even ",
    " than a stick of butter!\n\nScientists ",
    " studied pandas for many years to understand how to help them. Everyone loves these black and white animals ",
    " they are so cute and friendly."
  ],
